request.description:
Retrieve a list of all known article status values for a given Pocket user. 

Sample return value:
```
[
    {
        "pocket_user_id": "user@getpocket.com",
        "article_id": "12345",
        "offset_ms": 9876
    },
    {
        "pocket_user_id": "user@getpocket.com",
        "article_id": "123456",
        "offset_ms": 9876
    },
    {
        "pocket_user_id": "user@getpocket.com",
        "article_id": "1234567",
        "offset_ms": 98765
    },
]
```

If there are no article status records for this user, an empty list is returned.
